; Local work-context private registry example
; Managed by chezmoi — this file is a reference template.
; To activate: set WORK_NPM_REGISTRY in your local secrets and run chezmoi apply.
;
; Replace WORK_REGISTRY_URL with your registry URL, e.g.:
